overview.en: HOH（hell or heaven）The boundary agreement, established by a group of Silicon Valley blockchain enthusiasts and Silicon Valley's top technical teams, is designed to create an artificial intelligence sharing economy and a platform for artificial intelligence to truly serve society.
overview.zh: HOH（hell or heaven）界限协议由一群硅谷区块链爱好者和硅谷顶级技术团队共同建立，其设计愿景是打造一个人工智能共享经济体，让人工智能打造真正服务社会的平台。
